<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Deactivation - HTU LMS</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..12,200..1000;1,6..12,200..1000&family=Nunito:ital,wght@0,200..1000;1,200..1000&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: "Nunito Sans", sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #222222;
      }

      a {
        color: #0070f3;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #007bff;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Account Deactivation Request</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Dear <%= fullname %>,</p>
        <p>
          We have received your request to deactivate your HTU LMS account.
          Please note that your account will be deactivated in one week from the
          date of this email.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you did not make this request or have changed your mind, please
          ignore this email.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you have any questions or need further assistance, please feel free
          to contact us.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>
          If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us at
          <a href="mailto:michaelkpantiramp@gmail.com"
            >michaelkpantiramp@gmail.com</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
